title: Newport Jazz Festival founder George Wein turns 90
text: > Entertainment Newport Jazz Festival founder George Wein turns 90 FILE - In this Aug. 9, 2009 file photo, Newport Jazz Festival founder George Wein performs during a session with Christian McBride at the festival in Newport, R.I. On the eve of his 90th birthday, Wein took the stage Friday, Oct. 2, 2015 at Dizzy's Club Coca-Cola at Jazz at Lincoln Center to play piano and sing an original blues he had written for the occasion.(AP Photo/Joe Giblin, File)
